      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-prn-flg-int    not  = spaces
                     go to prn-rou-pri-711.
           perform   prn-ini-lr1-000      thru prn-ini-lr1-999        .
       prn-rou-pri-711.
