           multiply  w-stp-tot-cir-c02    by   13
                                        giving w-stp-tot-cir-inx      .
           add       w-stp-tot-cir-inx    to   w-stp-imp-vlb-pos      .
      *
           perform   stp-imp-vlb-000      thru stp-imp-vlb-999        .
